        <Parent_String>Thai pottery styles [300019233], Thai (culture or style) [300019199], Southeast Asian [300120146], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
